subtests.name: Property list-style value 'none' computes to 'outside none none'
Property list-style value 'inside' computes to 'inside none disc'
Property list-style value 'url("https://example.com/")' computes to 'outside url("https://example.com/") disc'
Property list-style value 'square' computes to 'outside none square'
Property list-style value 'inside url("https://example.com/") square' computes to 'inside url("https://example.com/") square'
